1
00:01:25,510 --> 00:01:29,880
[Coroner's Diary]

2
00:01:30,900 --> 00:01:33,920
[Episode 28]

3
00:01:38,320 --> 00:01:39,229
Little Wan'er,

4
00:01:39,250 --> 00:01:41,009
that was a close one.

5
00:01:41,039 --> 00:01:44,039
Yan Li told me
Minister Li is very high-maintenance.

6
00:01:44,350 --> 00:01:46,580
If he files a complaint against you
to the Emperor,

7
00:01:46,580 --> 00:01:48,950
you'll lose access to
the Ministry of Justice.

8
00:01:48,950 --> 00:01:51,030
We'd better stay away from him.

9
00:01:51,759 --> 00:01:53,560
I should've been more cautious.

10
00:01:53,759 --> 00:01:56,650
I must not drag you and Yan Li
into danger again.

11
00:01:57,090 --> 00:01:57,870
I

12
00:01:58,110 --> 00:01:59,950
used to be a loner.

13
00:02:00,070 --> 00:02:01,730
I wasn't considerate enough.

14
00:02:02,030 --> 00:02:02,950
From now on,

15
00:02:02,970 --> 00:02:04,670
I can't put you guys at risk again.

16
00:02:04,670 --> 00:02:06,620
It's not as serious as you imagine.

17
00:02:07,370 --> 00:02:08,449
Besides,

18
00:02:08,560 --> 00:02:10,550
I'm glad to go through trouble with you.

19
00:02:10,550 --> 00:02:11,950
But it upsets me.

20
00:02:12,560 --> 00:02:13,420
Little Wan'er,

21
00:02:14,040 --> 00:02:16,410
ever since the day I met you,

22
00:02:17,450 --> 00:02:19,910
I've always known
you're no ordinary woman.

23
00:02:20,640 --> 00:02:21,490
I only hope

24
00:02:22,310 --> 00:02:24,440
that you won't be held back by anything

25
00:02:24,720 --> 00:02:26,920
and that you'll always stride forward.

26
00:02:27,040 --> 00:02:29,660
If you're constrained
by the fear of implicating me,

27
00:02:29,660 --> 00:02:31,660
that will truly break my heart.

28
00:02:37,370 --> 00:02:39,360
I can't believe I just said those words.

29
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:41,360
What a rare and precious friend I am.

30
00:02:47,810 --> 00:02:48,410
Ning,

31
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:49,760
in fact...

32
00:02:50,600 --> 00:02:51,810
I'm not Qin Wan.

33
00:02:52,210 --> 00:02:53,579
I am Shen Yi's daughter,

34
00:02:53,880 --> 00:02:54,690
Shen Wan.

35
00:03:02,040 --> 00:03:02,650
You...

36
00:03:03,720 --> 00:03:04,790
Does Chi...

37
00:03:05,210 --> 00:03:06,370
He knew it long ago.

38
00:03:08,320 --> 00:03:08,960
You...

39
00:03:09,070 --> 00:03:10,690
I'm concealing my real identity

40
00:03:10,690 --> 00:03:13,220
for the purpose of
clearing my father's name.

41
00:03:14,090 --> 00:03:15,270
Are you crazy?

42
00:03:15,480 --> 00:03:17,210
How could you just blurt it out?

43
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:18,880
You treat me with sincerity,

44
00:03:19,320 --> 00:03:21,450
so I don't want to deceive you anymore.

45
00:03:22,250 --> 00:03:23,410
That doesn't mean

46
00:03:23,410 --> 00:03:25,740
I'd like to know such an important secret.

47
00:03:26,370 --> 00:03:28,170
Keeping secrets is exhausting.

48
00:03:28,280 --> 00:03:29,040
Besides,

49
00:03:29,720 --> 00:03:31,780
why should I care about your surname?

50
00:03:32,130 --> 00:03:33,460
Can a different surname

51
00:03:33,850 --> 00:03:35,310
change who you really are?

52
00:03:36,530 --> 00:03:37,720
I'm still me.

53
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:40,290
I'm the same girl you met on day one.

54
00:03:41,320 --> 00:03:42,720
That's all I need to know.

55
00:03:43,560 --> 00:03:44,430
I'll pretend

56
00:03:44,750 --> 00:03:46,320
not to have heard any of that.

57
00:03:46,320 --> 00:03:47,410
From now on,

58
00:03:47,410 --> 00:03:49,370
we'll behave the exact same way as before.

59
00:03:49,370 --> 00:03:50,170
Since Shen...

60
00:03:51,570 --> 00:03:53,829
your father was an upstanding official,

61
00:03:53,880 --> 00:03:56,340
I won't blame you
for telling me this secret.

62
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:00,720
Then,

63
00:04:00,970 --> 00:04:01,970
Yan Li...

64
00:04:03,200 --> 00:04:04,600
Don't tell him the truth.

65
00:04:04,810 --> 00:04:05,690
What if he gets drunk someday

66
00:04:05,690 --> 00:04:07,220
and has a slip of the tongue?

67
00:04:08,130 --> 00:04:08,850
Well,

68
00:04:09,130 --> 00:04:10,990
I'll let you in on another secret.

69
00:04:11,420 --> 00:04:12,250
Actually...

70
00:04:12,760 --> 00:04:13,850
I'm older than you!

71
00:04:17,089 --> 00:04:18,920
Little Wan'er!

72
00:04:18,920 --> 00:04:20,029
You...

73
00:04:20,209 --> 00:04:22,540
You kept me in the dark
for the entire time!

74
00:04:22,570 --> 00:04:24,010
How could do you do that?

75
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:30,720
The Ministry of War

76
00:04:30,720 --> 00:04:31,570
plans to to shift the blame

77
00:04:31,570 --> 00:04:33,330
to those transport commissioners.

78
00:04:33,330 --> 00:04:34,720
Prince Cheng supervises
the Ministry of War.

79
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:36,180
This is probably his idea.

80
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:38,320
Tell the Dove Unit now

81
00:04:38,640 --> 00:04:40,360
to find out who in the Shuoxi Army is

82
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:41,220
in contact with

83
00:04:41,360 --> 00:04:43,760
the Transport Bureau of Xibei Prefecture.

84
00:04:43,890 --> 00:04:46,010
I won't let Prince Cheng
easily get away

85
00:04:46,010 --> 00:04:47,450
by sacrificing a scapegoat.

86
00:04:47,450 --> 00:04:48,710
Master, do you suspect

87
00:04:49,240 --> 00:04:50,850
that there's a mole in the Shuoxi Army?

88
00:04:50,850 --> 00:04:51,770
If not,

89
00:04:52,600 --> 00:04:54,690
how could those transport commissioners

90
00:04:54,690 --> 00:04:56,650
have possibly snuck the moldy grains

91
00:04:56,650 --> 00:04:58,409
into the Shuoxi Army's granary?

92
00:04:58,409 --> 00:04:59,159
Shall we

93
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:01,660
inform Prince Rui of this matter?

94
00:05:05,650 --> 00:05:06,480
Father

95
00:05:06,850 --> 00:05:08,800
sees all his soldiers as family.

96
00:05:09,680 --> 00:05:10,720
If I tell him

97
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:13,480
that I'll conduct an investigation
inside the Shuoxi Army,

98
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:15,140
do you think he will believe me

99
00:05:15,160 --> 00:05:16,410
or scold me, accusing me of

100
00:05:16,410 --> 00:05:17,680
eagerly pursuing short-term interests

101
00:05:17,680 --> 00:05:19,480
and sabotaging our great cause?

102
00:05:20,010 --> 00:05:20,770
Master.

103
00:05:25,410 --> 00:05:26,010
Go.

104
00:05:27,920 --> 00:05:29,250
For the Shuoxi soldiers

105
00:05:30,280 --> 00:05:32,340
and the civilians in the border area,

106
00:05:33,120 --> 00:05:34,720
we must do what has to be done.

107
00:05:35,010 --> 00:05:35,650
Yes.

108
00:05:38,210 --> 00:05:40,570
Hu Dequan was responsible for
harvesting and producing ice.

109
00:05:40,570 --> 00:05:41,500
He usually lived

110
00:05:41,650 --> 00:05:44,120
in the backyard to watch the ice cellar
for the restaurant.

111
00:05:44,120 --> 00:05:45,180
Who would've known

112
00:05:45,570 --> 00:05:47,700
he'd freeze to death in the ice cellar?

113
00:05:47,920 --> 00:05:49,409
Did anyone touch anything here?

114
00:05:49,409 --> 00:05:49,970
No.

115
00:05:50,409 --> 00:05:52,240
The owner of Zuixian Restaurant
reported to the prefect's office

116
00:05:52,240 --> 00:05:53,480
right after he discovered the victim.

117
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:55,240
Nobody had come in here before we arrived.

118
00:05:55,240 --> 00:05:56,680
When you reached this place,

119
00:05:56,680 --> 00:05:59,159
was the first door of the ice cellar
already open?

120
00:05:59,159 --> 00:05:59,720
Yes.

121
00:06:15,300 --> 00:06:17,630
Take an impression of this footprint now.

122
00:06:27,090 --> 00:06:28,040
Could it be...

123
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:30,640
the victim's footprint?

124
00:06:30,720 --> 00:06:31,410
No.

125
00:06:31,850 --> 00:06:33,360
Judging from the victim's clothes

126
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:35,360
and the soil at the back of his shoes,

127
00:06:35,409 --> 00:06:37,920
the killer must've dragged
the victim's body into here

128
00:06:37,920 --> 00:06:39,450
after killing him outside.

129
00:06:39,480 --> 00:06:41,720
By then, the first door had been
open for a while.

130
00:06:41,720 --> 00:06:43,970
Some ice around had melted into water.

131
00:06:44,280 --> 00:06:46,720
So, the soil attached to the bottoms of
the murderer's shoes turned into mud,

132
00:06:46,720 --> 00:06:48,720
leaving footprints all along the way.

133
00:06:48,720 --> 00:06:51,240
But since he grabbed the victim
from behind as he walked in,

134
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:53,490
his footprints were wiped away
by the victim's body.

135
00:06:53,490 --> 00:06:54,800
When the murderer got to this spot,

136
00:06:54,800 --> 00:06:57,650
the mud on the bottoms of his shoes
was almost all gone.

137
00:06:57,650 --> 00:06:59,310
After he laid the victim down,

138
00:06:59,360 --> 00:07:00,800
for some reason,

139
00:07:00,800 --> 00:07:03,130
the victim's body exactly
covered the one last footprint,

140
00:07:03,130 --> 00:07:05,040
but he didn't realize it.

141
00:07:05,120 --> 00:07:07,530
Then, the murderer took his shoes off

142
00:07:07,530 --> 00:07:09,390
and left the ice cellar barefoot.

143
00:07:20,120 --> 00:07:21,320
I just won't tell you.

144
00:07:21,810 --> 00:07:23,070
Little Wan'er carries

145
00:07:23,070 --> 00:07:24,870
the legacy of ancestral wisdom.

146
00:07:35,720 --> 00:07:37,530
The ice punishment...

147
00:07:40,010 --> 00:07:41,210
The killings were indeed arranged

148
00:07:41,210 --> 00:07:42,650
according to the Seven-Layered Inferno.

149
00:07:42,650 --> 00:07:43,510
Your Highness,

150
00:07:43,900 --> 00:07:44,700
the problem is

151
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:47,900
the Black Unrighteous Flower
is nowhere to be seen.

152
00:08:02,450 --> 00:08:03,650
Close the door now.

153
00:08:03,650 --> 00:08:04,510
Close the door!

154
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:52,520
The ice punishment

155
00:08:52,520 --> 00:08:53,480
is designed for

156
00:08:53,480 --> 00:08:55,340
those who betray their families.

157
00:08:55,930 --> 00:08:57,450
Who on earth did this?

158
00:08:57,880 --> 00:08:58,580
Ning,

159
00:08:58,640 --> 00:08:59,760
go with Yan Li to find out

160
00:08:59,760 --> 00:09:01,690
if the victim got along with
his family and friends.

161
00:09:01,690 --> 00:09:02,240
Got it!

162
00:09:07,400 --> 00:09:09,530
What exactly is going on between them?

163
00:09:10,930 --> 00:09:11,690
Wait up!

164
00:09:12,720 --> 00:09:13,520
Sir,

165
00:09:14,170 --> 00:09:16,850
someone died in the ice cellar
of your restaurant.

166
00:09:16,850 --> 00:09:18,930
I'm afraid your business will be affected.

167
00:09:18,930 --> 00:09:20,660
That's what I'm worried about.

168
00:09:20,970 --> 00:09:22,120
When Hu Dequan was alive,

169
00:09:22,120 --> 00:09:23,720
he was already a menace.

170
00:09:23,720 --> 00:09:25,480
Now, even his death is causing me trouble.

171
00:09:25,480 --> 00:09:26,540
If I had known this,

172
00:09:26,970 --> 00:09:29,430
I wouldn't have kindly
taken him in at first.

173
00:09:29,640 --> 00:09:31,290
It sounds like

174
00:09:31,290 --> 00:09:33,620
Hu Dequan wasn't
much of a nice guy, was he?

175
00:09:34,330 --> 00:09:36,850
He used to work as a purchaser
for the restaurant.

176
00:09:36,850 --> 00:09:38,690
His gambling addiction

177
00:09:38,690 --> 00:09:40,090
got him into heavy debts.

178
00:09:40,520 --> 00:09:42,980
Then, he sold his only daughter
to a brothel.

179
00:09:43,290 --> 00:09:45,550
But instead of learning a lesson from it,

180
00:09:45,850 --> 00:09:48,030
he gambled again and lost all that money.

181
00:09:48,030 --> 00:09:50,210
What's worse, the banker broke his legs.

182
00:09:50,210 --> 00:09:53,170
He could barely make a living,
so he turned to me for help.

183
00:09:53,170 --> 00:09:54,400
Out of pity,

184
00:09:54,400 --> 00:09:56,200
I let him stay in the back quarters

185
00:09:56,200 --> 00:09:58,860
to look after the ice cellar
for the restaurant.

186
00:10:00,680 --> 00:10:01,710
Sir, do you know

187
00:10:01,980 --> 00:10:03,190
which brothel

188
00:10:03,210 --> 00:10:05,210
Hu Dequan sold his daughter to?

189
00:10:05,660 --> 00:10:06,780
I think it was...

190
00:10:07,210 --> 00:10:08,450
Fengqi House.

191
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:25,260
Don't, Your Highness!

192
00:10:26,780 --> 00:10:27,510
It's okay.

193
00:10:27,760 --> 00:10:29,820
This powder is burned Datura leaves.

194
00:10:29,850 --> 00:10:31,520
It's available at any pharmacy.

195
00:10:31,520 --> 00:10:32,850
Datura leaves?

196
00:10:33,520 --> 00:10:34,850
Does Your Highness mean

197
00:10:35,050 --> 00:10:37,000
the murderer drugged the victim first

198
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:38,480
before dragging him into the ice cellar

199
00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:40,280
and letting him freeze to death?

200
00:10:41,210 --> 00:10:43,720
The smile on the victim's face
is the best proof.

201
00:10:43,720 --> 00:10:45,290
Before a man freezes to death,

202
00:10:45,290 --> 00:10:47,210
the blood in him
would start circulating slowly.

203
00:10:47,210 --> 00:10:49,050
Delightful hallucinations are
likely to occur

204
00:10:49,050 --> 00:10:51,050
to relieve the man of physical pain.

205
00:10:51,210 --> 00:10:53,050
That's why smiles tend to
appear on the faces

206
00:10:53,050 --> 00:10:54,580
of those freezing to death.

207
00:10:54,970 --> 00:10:56,480
There are only undergarments
on the victim.

208
00:10:56,480 --> 00:10:59,450
It suggests that he was going to bed
when he was drugged.

209
00:10:59,450 --> 00:11:00,480
In his abode,

210
00:11:00,690 --> 00:11:03,420
there should be residue of
burned Datura leaves.

211
00:11:03,600 --> 00:11:04,170
Got it.

212
00:11:25,570 --> 00:11:28,230
The Datura powder was
placed in the candle wick.

213
00:11:28,850 --> 00:11:29,710
Little Wan'er.

214
00:11:32,280 --> 00:11:33,170
We found

215
00:11:33,170 --> 00:11:35,400
where Hu Dequan sold his daughter to—

216
00:11:35,400 --> 00:11:36,450
Fengqi House.

217
00:11:37,050 --> 00:11:38,850
The first victim also visited

218
00:11:38,850 --> 00:11:39,760
Fengqi House.

219
00:11:39,830 --> 00:11:41,830
The second victim, Zhao Jiaxu,

220
00:11:41,860 --> 00:11:43,690
had a mistress from Fengqi House.

221
00:11:43,690 --> 00:11:45,210
The third victim was
connected to Fengqi House too.

222
00:11:45,210 --> 00:11:46,340
This is our finding.

223
00:11:47,810 --> 00:11:48,520
The link

224
00:11:48,520 --> 00:11:51,180
among these victims
has finally been revealed.

225
00:11:57,760 --> 00:11:59,170
What's the matter, Little Wan'er?

226
00:11:59,170 --> 00:12:01,230
Did you catch a cold in the ice cellar?

227
00:12:01,290 --> 00:12:02,950
I'm usually better than that.

228
00:12:03,210 --> 00:12:06,340
But I've been working cases non-stop
during these days.

229
00:12:08,000 --> 00:12:09,530
Greetings, Your Highness.

230
00:12:10,810 --> 00:12:11,450
Chi.

231
00:12:11,720 --> 00:12:12,360
Chi.

232
00:12:24,090 --> 00:12:25,120
What are you doing?

233
00:12:25,120 --> 00:12:26,360
It was just a few coughs.

234
00:12:26,360 --> 00:12:27,210
Put me down.

235
00:12:27,820 --> 00:12:28,750
Don't act tough.

236
00:12:31,930 --> 00:12:33,190
Everyone, attention!

237
00:12:33,810 --> 00:12:34,740
Close your eyes!

238
00:12:34,960 --> 00:12:35,690
Turn around!

239
00:12:36,670 --> 00:12:38,070
Do you know when

240
00:12:38,120 --> 00:12:39,090
to avert your eyes?

241
00:12:39,090 --> 00:12:39,810
Yes!

242
00:12:39,810 --> 00:12:41,110
Do you know what

243
00:12:41,330 --> 00:12:42,210
not to say?

244
00:12:42,210 --> 00:12:43,000
Yes!

245
00:12:52,360 --> 00:12:53,810
Young man,

246
00:12:53,810 --> 00:12:55,930
well done. A bright future awaits you.

247
00:12:55,930 --> 00:12:57,130
Thank Your Highness.

248
00:12:57,180 --> 00:12:58,210
I was only doing my job.

249
00:12:58,210 --> 00:12:59,000
Very good.

250
00:13:02,090 --> 00:13:03,420
What are you looking at?

251
00:13:04,600 --> 00:13:05,480
What's wrong?

252
00:13:05,880 --> 00:13:07,290
Your eyes fixed on him,

253
00:13:07,520 --> 00:13:09,780
like a hungry wolf staring at a fat sheep.

254
00:13:10,050 --> 00:13:11,570
That's not true!

255
00:13:12,970 --> 00:13:13,900
Close your eyes.

256
00:13:14,210 --> 00:13:14,940
Turn around.

257
00:13:17,870 --> 00:13:19,770
Do you know when

258
00:13:20,090 --> 00:13:21,150
to avert your eyes?

259
00:13:34,170 --> 00:13:34,640
Come on.

260
00:13:43,340 --> 00:13:44,170
I prepared

261
00:13:44,170 --> 00:13:46,570
this medicine for you
in the Herbal Garden.

262
00:13:47,260 --> 00:13:47,910
I tried it.

263
00:13:48,120 --> 00:13:49,330
It cures a cold fast.

264
00:13:56,090 --> 00:13:56,820
Here you are.

265
00:14:10,760 --> 00:14:12,520
How's the military provision case going?

266
00:14:12,520 --> 00:14:14,090
I've found out everything they let out.

267
00:14:14,090 --> 00:14:15,290
As for what they don't want to let out,

268
00:14:15,290 --> 00:14:17,360
I'll have it revealed sooner or later.

269
00:14:17,360 --> 00:14:18,530
Just don't worry.

270
00:14:20,400 --> 00:14:23,930
I told Ning about my real identity.

271
00:14:25,210 --> 00:14:26,000
I see.

272
00:14:26,720 --> 00:14:28,040
Get some sleep now.

273
00:14:28,170 --> 00:14:29,520
You'll feel better after sweating a bit.

274
00:14:29,520 --> 00:14:30,120
Come here.

275
00:14:43,300 --> 00:14:47,060
[Qin Residence]

276
00:15:01,360 --> 00:15:02,480
My Lady, you finally woke up.

277
00:15:02,480 --> 00:15:03,810
Are you feeling better?

278
00:15:07,400 --> 00:15:08,360
Come with me now.

279
00:15:08,360 --> 00:15:09,820
People have been waiting.

280
00:15:27,820 --> 00:15:28,980
Just like Yingqi,

281
00:15:29,410 --> 00:15:30,980
