299
00:16:19,040 --> 00:16:20,930
investigating the brothel, so don't worry.

300
00:16:20,930 --> 00:16:21,460
Let's go.

301
00:16:22,240 --> 00:16:22,880
Wan,

302
00:16:22,920 --> 00:16:23,540
