310
00:16:41,690 --> 00:16:43,820
I was planning to pick you up tomorrow.

311
00:16:45,880 --> 00:16:47,970
Thank you so much, Lord Yan,

312
00:16:48,330 --> 00:16:49,690
for pulling me out of

313
00:16:49,760 --> 00:16:51,750
that abyss of misery.

314
00:16:52,690 --> 00:16:54,640
He now lives in the side chamber
of the front quarters.

315
00:16:54,640 --> 00:16:55,840
Nobody else knows it.

316
00:16:56,120 --> 00:16:57,120
Without your token,

317
