he can't step out of the premises.

318
00:17:02,050 --> 00:17:05,670
I heard the ice punishment
had appeared today.

319
00:17:05,770 --> 00:17:07,490
I'd better get back to my room

320
00:17:07,490 --> 00:17:10,119
to ponder over the cases in Guanyin Town.

321
00:17:11,200 --> 00:17:13,599
That way, a certain someone will stop

322
00:17:13,599 --> 00:17:17,119
calling me a mercenary fraud.

323
00:17:39,680 --> 00:17:40,530
Don't be afraid.

324
00:17:40,530 --> 00:17:41,260
I'm here.

325
00:17:49,490 --> 00:17:50,880
Ning,

326
00:17:52,250 --> 00:17:54,680
