It's gold!

336
00:18:20,440 --> 00:18:21,250
Do you want it?

337
00:18:22,090 --> 00:18:22,770
Yes.

338
00:18:22,820 --> 00:18:24,580
Those who faithfully do as I say

339
00:18:25,010 --> 00:18:26,160
