357
00:19:10,720 --> 00:19:11,680
So do I.

358
00:19:12,770 --> 00:19:13,570
Very good.

359
00:19:14,490 --> 00:19:16,150
Here comes the last question.

360
00:19:16,400 --> 00:19:18,120
Those who know Hu Dequan,

361
00:19:19,000 --> 00:19:19,960
step forward.

362
00:19:30,320 --> 00:19:31,880
The rest of you may leave.

363
00:19:31,960 --> 00:19:32,920
You three stay.

364
00:19:37,490 --> 00:19:38,440
Let's figure out

365
00:19:38,440 --> 00:19:39,490
who else

366
00:19:39,520 --> 00:19:42,350
has asked you about these three people.

367
00:19:55,770 --> 00:19:57,360
This used to be a high wall.

368
00:19:58,290 --> 00:20:01,150
After my father and Qin Liang
became close friends,

369
00:20:02,060 --> 00:20:04,190
it began to be decorated with flowers.

370
