A small door was opened there
for convenience.

371
00:20:14,490 --> 00:20:16,820
They are secret guards from the Dove Unit.

372
00:20:41,530 --> 00:20:42,600
I thought

373
00:20:44,810 --> 00:20:46,730
this house had been confiscated.

374
00:20:47,770 --> 00:20:49,970
Confiscated properties can be resold.

375
00:20:50,600 --> 00:20:52,290
Lord Shen was an honest officer.

376
00:20:52,290 --> 00:20:54,120
This old house is in a remote location.

377
00:20:54,120 --> 00:20:55,810
Nobles have no interest in it.

378
00:20:56,770 --> 00:20:58,370
Plus, it is related to a case.

379
00:20:58,530 --> 00:20:59,960
So, I was able to buy it

380
00:21:00,440 --> 00:21:01,900
in the name of a brokerage.

381
00:21:04,290 --> 00:21:05,490
Cry it out if you want.

382
00:21:05,600 --> 00:21:07,400
I know you're upset. Vent it out.

383
00:21:10,200 --> 00:21:12,260
I'm just happy to get back what I lost.

384
00:21:12,730 --> 00:21:13,640
I'm not upset.

385
00:21:19,900 --> 00:21:22,470
I dreamed about this tree on the carriage.

386
00:21:23,770 --> 00:21:24,770
When I was little,

387
00:21:25,400 --> 00:21:27,400
when I didn't want to do needlework,

388
00:21:27,530 --> 00:21:29,050
I'd climb up this tree.

389
00:21:29,680 --> 00:21:31,400
My mother, furiously holding a ruler,

390
00:21:31,400 --> 00:21:33,330
would stomp her feet on the ground.

391
00:21:38,850 --> 00:21:40,730
Being punished by a loving mother

392
00:21:42,600 --> 00:21:44,730
is actually a thing to be grateful for.

393
00:21:48,160 --> 00:21:50,160
If Princess Consort Rui were alive,

394
00:21:50,440 --> 00:21:52,700
I'm sure she would be just like my mother.

395
00:21:52,920 --> 00:21:53,920
She would love you

396
00:21:54,570 --> 00:21:56,600
and cherish you with all her heart.

397
00:21:57,440 --> 00:21:58,960
If you misbehaved,

398
00:21:59,330 --> 00:22:01,360
she would discipline you harshly.

399
00:22:13,260 --> 00:22:14,520
Today, I read the files

400
00:22:16,140 --> 00:22:18,770
about my father and Prince Jin
in the Court of Judicial Review.

401
00:22:18,770 --> 00:22:19,810
I know what crimes

402
00:22:19,810 --> 00:22:21,680
they fabricated against my father,

403
00:22:21,680 --> 00:22:23,610
and how they slandered Prince Jin.

404
00:22:24,680 --> 00:22:26,920
This is a battle we must win

405
00:22:27,200 --> 00:22:28,680
at all costs.

406
00:22:29,730 --> 00:22:30,640
Did you notice

407
00:22:30,640 --> 00:22:32,240
anything odd in those files?

408
00:22:32,360 --> 00:22:33,690
According to the files,

409
00:22:35,050 --> 00:22:36,250
Prince Jin confessed

410
00:22:36,360 --> 00:22:39,280
that he raped and killed Consort Jin
when he was drunk.

411
00:22:39,280 --> 00:22:40,810
But that was not a real confession.

412
00:22:40,810 --> 00:22:42,440
Prince Jin's silence
during the interrogation

413
00:22:42,440 --> 00:22:43,300
was recorded as

414
00:22:43,510 --> 00:22:45,240
"unable to provide an answer."

415
00:22:45,640 --> 00:22:46,700
The files also say,

416
00:22:47,090 --> 00:22:48,670
Prince Jin was standing beside

417
00:22:48,670 --> 00:22:50,400
Consort Jin's body
with a dagger in his hand.

418
00:22:50,400 --> 00:22:52,900
How could someone drunk enough
to commit those heinous crimes

419
00:22:52,900 --> 00:22:54,920
have possibly stood steadily on his feet?

420
00:22:54,920 --> 00:22:56,720
Then in the file about Lord Shen,

421
00:22:56,850 --> 00:22:58,850
did you notice anything suspicious?

422
00:22:58,850 --> 00:23:00,050
The file says

423
00:23:01,090 --> 00:23:03,160
my father hid some physical evidence
of Prince Jin's case.

424
00:23:03,160 --> 00:23:03,810
But it doesn't

425
00:23:03,810 --> 00:23:05,600
specify any items.

426
00:23:06,250 --> 00:23:07,450
Just like Prince Jin,

427
00:23:08,330 --> 00:23:09,920
my father confessed to his crimes

428
00:23:09,920 --> 00:23:11,860
by being "unable to provide an answer."

429
00:23:11,860 --> 00:23:12,900
Li Muyun must've

430
00:23:12,920 --> 00:23:14,650
tampered with those two files.

431
00:23:14,770 --> 00:23:15,520
My father and Prince Jin

432
00:23:15,520 --> 00:23:17,380
would never commit those crimes.

433
00:23:17,850 --> 00:23:20,250
I'm worried this might be
a trap set up by Li Muyun.

434
00:23:20,250 --> 00:23:21,200
If he discovers

435
00:23:21,640 --> 00:23:24,010
you've read Lord Shen's
and Prince Jin's files,

436
00:23:24,010 --> 00:23:25,670
and reports it to the Emperor,

437
00:23:25,850 --> 00:23:26,640
I'm afraid

438
00:23:27,090 --> 00:23:29,220
we'll have to flee and never come back.

439
00:23:29,960 --> 00:23:31,820
I shouldn't have acted so rashly.

440
00:23:33,600 --> 00:23:35,810
Would Li Muyun go to such great lengths

441
00:23:36,060 --> 00:23:37,450
only to test us?

442
00:23:38,340 --> 00:23:39,470
I'm afraid he also wants to identify

443
00:23:39,470 --> 00:23:41,600
those attempting to
reopen Prince Jin's case

444
00:23:41,600 --> 00:23:42,930
and eliminate them all.

445
00:23:43,640 --> 00:23:45,090
Then I'll stay low for a while

446
00:23:45,090 --> 00:23:46,360
to avoid alerting him.

447
00:23:48,250 --> 00:23:48,960
Be patient.

448
00:23:49,400 --> 00:23:51,930
We're getting closer and closer
to the truth.

449
00:23:57,050 --> 00:23:57,920
Are you okay?

450
00:23:57,920 --> 00:23:59,360
It hurts.

451
00:23:59,450 --> 00:24:00,600
I'm in pain.

452
00:24:00,600 --> 00:24:01,730
I didn't know it'd break...

453
00:24:01,730 --> 00:24:03,560
Stop talking. It's all your fault.

454
00:24:03,560 --> 00:24:04,490
My bottom hurts terribly.

455
00:24:04,490 --> 00:24:05,200
Put me down now.

456
00:24:05,200 --> 00:24:06,200
Okay, okay.

457
00:24:12,470 --> 00:24:13,950
Master, Your Highness.

458
00:24:14,530 --> 00:24:16,060
What are you two doing here?

459
00:24:19,200 --> 00:24:19,960
Well...

460
00:24:19,960 --> 00:24:20,810
You say it.

461
00:24:22,360 --> 00:24:24,170
I was trying to build a swing chair

462
00:24:24,170 --> 00:24:25,170
in the courtyard.

463
00:24:25,960 --> 00:24:27,230
Unexpectedly,

464
00:24:27,400 --> 00:24:29,530
