465
00:24:29,530 --> 00:24:30,660
It broke in the end.

466
00:24:32,570 --> 00:24:33,770
Two people, huh?

467
00:24:35,010 --> 00:24:36,060
Your Highness!

468
00:24:37,090 --> 00:24:39,160
Why did you have to be so explicit?

469
00:24:49,010 --> 00:24:49,490
Wan,

470
00:24:50,090 --> 00:24:51,090
go check on Fuling first.

471
00:24:51,090 --> 00:24:52,420
Go to bed early tonight.

472
00:24:52,730 --> 00:24:53,640
The butler

473
00:24:53,700 --> 00:24:55,360
