474
00:24:55,960 --> 00:24:57,770
You and General Bai should get going now.

475
00:24:57,770 --> 00:24:59,100
Don't worry about me...

476
00:24:59,400 --> 00:25:00,090
and Fuling.

477
00:25:06,200 --> 00:25:07,360
Good for you.

478
00:25:07,640 --> 00:25:09,770
Why didn't you share this idea with me?

479
00:25:10,480 --> 00:25:11,040
Master,

480
00:25:11,070 --> 00:25:12,700
