a carriage as a gift already.

481
00:25:12,700 --> 00:25:14,550
I thought it was also time for me

482
00:25:15,330 --> 00:25:16,930
to please my darling, right?

483
00:25:17,960 --> 00:25:19,770
If I fail to delight my darling,

484
00:25:19,770 --> 00:25:21,850
