485
00:25:22,490 --> 00:25:23,620
What does that mean?

486
00:25:24,640 --> 00:25:27,200
Did Princess Yongci
say something to you, Master?

487
00:25:27,200 --> 00:25:28,730
Please don't be mad, Master.

488
00:25:28,730 --> 00:25:29,990
If I come up with a good idea again,

489
00:25:29,990 --> 00:25:31,920
I promise I'll tell you right away!

490
00:25:35,290 --> 00:25:36,400
Let me get through.

491
00:25:38,010 --> 00:25:39,740
I told you to let me get through!

492
00:25:44,100 --> 00:25:45,670
Let go of me. I'm Zhang Dongxuan.

493
00:25:45,670 --> 00:25:48,400
I have something urgent
to tell Princess Yongci!

494
00:25:48,610 --> 00:25:52,340
Nobody can enter the inner quarters
without Master's permission.

495
00:25:52,730 --> 00:25:53,670
Release him.

496
00:26:03,090 --> 00:26:03,770
Your Highness,

497
00:26:03,770 --> 00:26:05,330
where did you recruit these people from?

498
00:26:05,330 --> 00:26:06,960
They assaulted me
without knowing who I am.

499
00:26:06,960 --> 00:26:07,850
If I had been hurt,

500
00:26:07,850 --> 00:26:10,140
let's see how you're going to
explain to Princess Yongci!

501
00:26:10,140 --> 00:26:11,060
Cut the crap.

502
00:26:11,600 --> 00:26:13,600
Why do you want to meet the princess?

503
00:26:24,810 --> 00:26:27,680
I figured out a pattern by studying

504
00:26:27,680 --> 00:26:29,850
the three murders in Guanyin Town.

505
00:26:30,770 --> 00:26:32,500
You're better than I expected.

506
00:26:32,570 --> 00:26:33,800
A man's life will be endangered.

507
00:26:33,800 --> 00:26:36,310
Now is not the time to taunt me,
Your Highness.

508
00:26:36,310 --> 00:26:37,370
My calculation results

509
00:26:37,370 --> 00:26:40,430
indicate that the fourth killing
will happen tonight.

510
00:26:40,880 --> 00:26:42,480
The fourth killing tonight?

511
00:26:42,770 --> 00:26:44,430
One more than in Guanyin Town?

512
00:26:46,640 --> 00:26:47,850
Yes.

513
00:26:48,140 --> 00:26:50,930
My deductions were made
based on the calendar and the regular way

514
00:26:50,930 --> 00:26:52,850
that the leader
of the Heavenly Way Society acts.

515
00:26:52,850 --> 00:26:54,640
But I can't guarantee the accuracy

516
00:26:54,640 --> 00:26:56,010
of these results.

517
00:26:56,290 --> 00:26:58,250
Following the key principles
of the calendar,

518
00:26:58,250 --> 00:26:59,640
I deduced seven dates.

519
00:26:59,640 --> 00:27:01,250
Tonight, it'll be time

520
00:27:03,960 --> 00:27:05,360
for the fire punishment.

521
00:27:05,530 --> 00:27:06,730
If Your Highness is convinced,

522
00:27:06,730 --> 00:27:07,810
please get prepared soon.

523
00:27:07,810 --> 00:27:08,600
But if not,

524
00:27:08,600 --> 00:27:10,200
then forget what I just said.

525
00:27:14,110 --> 00:27:14,700
Now,

526
00:27:15,530 --> 00:27:17,680
it is not confirmed
if a murder will happen,

527
00:27:17,680 --> 00:27:19,480
or where and when it will happen.

528
00:27:19,640 --> 00:27:21,010
We must patrol
throughout the night,

529
00:27:21,010 --> 00:27:22,960
so as to discover any fires
as early as possible.

530
00:27:22,960 --> 00:27:23,960
If a fire happens,

531
00:27:24,780 --> 00:27:25,780
save lives first!

532
00:27:25,990 --> 00:27:26,640
Yes!

533
00:27:31,330 --> 00:27:32,090
Set out!

534
00:27:32,090 --> 00:27:32,670
Let's go!

535
00:27:56,160 --> 00:27:57,160
It's 11 p.m. now.

536
00:27:57,800 --> 00:27:59,250
Nothing has happened yet.

537
00:27:59,250 --> 00:27:59,920
Indeed.

538
00:28:04,160 --> 00:28:05,220
What's that place?

539
00:28:06,120 --> 00:28:08,400
That's the Jade Street in the East Market.

540
00:28:08,400 --> 00:28:09,360
Sound the alarm.

541
00:28:09,420 --> 00:28:11,110
Send the fire rescue team there!

542
00:28:11,110 --> 00:28:12,040
Sound the alarm!

543
00:28:45,600 --> 00:28:46,800
How is this possible?

544
00:28:47,330 --> 00:28:48,260
It can't be true.

545
00:28:48,680 --> 00:28:49,610
It can't be true!

546
00:28:59,680 --> 00:29:00,480
Wan.

547
00:29:07,200 --> 00:29:08,050
Yan Chi!

548
00:29:12,800 --> 00:29:13,530
Wan.

549
00:29:21,090 --> 00:29:22,420
Did you have a bad dream?

550
00:29:22,680 --> 00:29:24,680
I dreamed you were trapped in a fire.

551
00:29:25,010 --> 00:29:26,050
I was terrified.

552
00:29:27,360 --> 00:29:29,820
There really is
a mental rapport between us.

553
00:29:32,860 --> 00:29:33,730
What happened?

554
00:29:34,580 --> 00:29:36,780
Someone received the fire punishment.

555
00:29:39,500 --> 00:29:41,890
Look, it's completely ruined.

556
00:29:41,920 --> 00:29:43,780
I wonder how that man's doing now.

557
00:29:44,160 --> 00:29:44,960
Shouchang!

558
00:29:45,600 --> 00:29:46,810
Shouchang!

559
00:29:47,510 --> 00:29:49,710
Shouchang, Mom is here!

560
00:29:50,160 --> 00:29:51,730
-Shouchang!
-Ma'am...

561
00:29:51,730 --> 00:29:54,730
