00:29:55,730 --> 00:29:57,330
That's the victim's mother.

564
00:29:58,050 --> 00:30:00,560
The murderer only spread oil
around the victim.

565
00:30:00,560 --> 00:30:03,200
That's why the fire didn't reach
farther places quickly.

566
00:30:03,200 --> 00:30:04,570
Too bad that I arrived too late.

567
00:30:04,570 --> 00:30:05,970
I wasn't able to save him.

568
00:30:13,010 --> 00:30:15,000
Mr. Wang was always meticulous.

569
00:30:15,320 --> 00:30:17,380
How did he let a fire start in his shop?

570
00:30:17,920 --> 00:30:20,160
Could it be related to the recent murders?

571
00:30:20,160 --> 00:30:21,250
That's impossible.

572
00:30:21,250 --> 00:30:23,810
I heard the killer would only
go after bad people.

573
00:30:23,810 --> 00:30:25,290
Mr. Wang was very nice.

574
00:30:25,290 --> 00:30:27,250
How did he get in this kind of trouble?

575
00:30:27,250 --> 00:30:29,120
Maybe he had a dark side you don't know.

576
00:30:29,120 --> 00:30:29,880
Cut it out!

577
00:30:30,530 --> 00:30:31,640
Only a few of us know

578
00:30:31,640 --> 00:30:33,300
the details of these murders.

579
00:30:33,600 --> 00:30:35,530
How did these civilians get to know

580
00:30:35,640 --> 00:30:38,700
that the previous victims were
considered bad people?

581
00:30:38,960 --> 00:30:41,360
Those in the Heavenly Way Society
have the details too.

582
00:30:41,360 --> 00:30:43,960
I suppose they'd let out
the victims' information

583
00:30:43,960 --> 00:30:46,440
before executing them
in the name of serving justice.

584
00:30:46,440 --> 00:30:47,880
If someone in the capital is

585
00:30:47,880 --> 00:30:49,530
using the Heavenly Way Society

586
00:30:49,530 --> 00:30:51,640
to eliminate opponents
and confuse the Emperor,

587
00:30:51,640 --> 00:30:52,700
then I'm afraid

588
00:30:52,850 --> 00:30:54,880
the capital will soon plunge into chaos.

589
00:30:54,880 --> 00:30:56,480
But now we're short of leads.

590
00:30:57,010 --> 00:30:59,410
God knows
when the murderer will be caught.

591
00:30:59,810 --> 00:31:00,470
Don't fret.

592
00:31:00,810 --> 00:31:02,090
That's just a speculation.

593
00:31:02,090 --> 00:31:03,930
Perhaps the situation
won't develop that way.

594
00:31:03,930 --> 00:31:05,460
All you need to do is focus on

595
00:31:05,550 --> 00:31:06,750
searching for leads.

596
00:31:06,940 --> 00:31:08,400
I'll take care of the rest.

597
00:31:08,920 --> 00:31:09,600
Okay.

598
00:31:10,210 --> 00:31:12,740
The suspect of the military provision case
is being escorted to the capital.

599
00:31:12,740 --> 00:31:13,430
During these days,

600
00:31:13,430 --> 00:31:15,640
I may have to spend more time
in the Ministry of War.

601
00:31:15,640 --> 00:31:16,850
I'll have Bai Feng follow you around.

602
00:31:16,850 --> 00:31:17,530
Don't.

603
00:31:18,050 --> 00:31:19,490
That's a rather complicated case.

604
00:31:19,490 --> 00:31:20,880
You need a helpful aide.

605
00:31:21,440 --> 00:31:23,360
Yan Li and Ning are all I need.

606
00:31:31,210 --> 00:31:32,170
Water...

607
00:31:44,940 --> 00:31:45,980
Let me have a sip.

608
00:31:53,660 --> 00:31:54,180
You...

609
00:31:54,400 --> 00:31:55,040
You...

610
00:31:55,250 --> 00:31:56,140
You... you...

611
00:32:01,210 --> 00:32:02,450
What?

612
00:32:12,230 --> 00:32:13,510
What did you do to me?

613
00:32:16,560 --> 00:32:17,120
I...

614
00:32:17,290 --> 00:32:17,920
I...

615
00:32:18,600 --> 00:32:20,600
Stop disgusting me!

616
00:32:20,600 --> 00:32:21,290
I...

617
00:32:21,640 --> 00:32:23,440
What did you do to me?

618
00:32:23,770 --> 00:32:25,680
Did you deliberately get me drunk

619
00:32:25,740 --> 00:32:27,260
to take advantage of me?

620
00:32:27,400 --> 00:32:28,570
My goodness.

621
00:32:28,870 --> 00:32:30,870
Who took advantage of whom exactly?

622
00:32:34,090 --> 00:32:34,810
Come on!

623
00:32:35,910 --> 00:32:37,190
Drink it up.

624
00:32:37,570 --> 00:32:40,360
From now on,

625
00:32:40,360 --> 00:32:42,570
the world will know us as

626
00:32:42,570 --> 00:32:43,520
Yong,

627
00:32:43,970 --> 00:32:44,880
Li—

628
00:32:44,960 --> 00:32:47,050
the legendary detectives.

629
00:32:47,640 --> 00:32:48,340
Cheers!

630
00:32:50,110 --> 00:32:51,630
Yong and Li?

631
00:32:52,330 --> 00:32:53,390
We should be called

632
00:32:53,440 --> 00:32:54,410
the inseparable

633
00:32:54,770 --> 00:32:55,530
duo!

634
00:32:55,900 --> 00:32:56,600
Duo?

635
00:32:57,400 --> 00:32:58,120
Okay.

636
00:32:58,400 --> 00:33:00,940
Drink this up,
and we'll be the inseparable duo.

637
00:33:00,940 --> 00:33:03,340
If you don't, we'll just be Yong and Li!

638
00:33:03,570 --> 00:33:04,360
Deal!

639
00:33:04,850 --> 00:33:05,730
Bottoms up!

640
00:33:05,730 --> 00:33:06,390
Bottoms up!

641
00:33:34,600 --> 00:33:35,850
Li,

642
00:33:36,440 --> 00:33:37,460
listen.

643
00:33:38,120 --> 00:33:39,570
In fact...

644
00:33:40,830 --> 00:33:42,350
except Little Wan'er,

645
00:33:42,770 --> 00:33:45,180
you're the smartest person

646
00:33:45,200 --> 00:33:46,990
in the world.

647
00:33:47,440 --> 00:33:49,770
You bet I am. I know that.

648
00:33:49,770 --> 00:33:50,980
Besides,

649
00:33:51,360 --> 00:33:53,290
I feel

650
00:33:53,490 --> 00:33:55,300
the happiest...

651
00:33:55,460 --> 00:33:57,630
when I'm with you.

652
00:34:05,120 --> 00:34:06,120
Then...

653
00:34:07,490 --> 00:34:09,040
would you consider

654
00:34:10,389 --> 00:34:11,310
marrying me?

655
00:34:21,420 --> 00:34:23,139
I'm feeling terrible.

656
00:34:23,310 --> 00:34:25,800
Pat my back now, please.

657
00:34:31,650 --> 00:34:32,659
Yong and Li?

658
00:34:33,420 --> 00:34:35,230
What an awful name.

659
00:34:35,570 --> 00:34:36,830
I must be really drunk.

660
00:34:39,130 --> 00:34:39,850
Do you

661
00:34:40,400 --> 00:34:42,400
really not remember anything?

662
00:34:44,830 --> 00:34:46,159
What should I remember?

663
00:34:46,400 --> 00:34:49,659
All I can remember
is that I felt terribly dizzy yesterday.

664
00:34:51,080 --> 00:34:52,440
Just because I can't recall anything

665
00:34:52,440 --> 00:34:53,610
doesn't mean you can fool me.

666
00:34:53,610 --> 00:34:55,469
I have zero tolerance for deceit!

667
00:34:57,850 --> 00:34:59,650
What can I gain from fooling you?

668
00:35:01,000 --> 00:35:02,550
Look at my face.

669
00:35:02,840 --> 00:35:03,710
I'm the one who suffered a loss.

670
00:35:03,710 --> 00:35:05,290
Stop talking nonsense!

671
00:35:07,320 --> 00:35:09,040
You just won't admit
you took advantage of me, right?

672
00:35:09,040 --> 00:35:10,610
Let's go back to the palace

673
00:35:10,610 --> 00:35:12,440
to meet the Empress Dowager
and the Grand Princess now.

674
00:35:12,440 --> 00:35:14,330
We'll tell them we slept outside
last night

675
00:35:14,330 --> 00:35:16,660
and ask them to decide
which of us is right.

676
00:35:18,690 --> 00:35:20,690
If you ever let out a word about this,

677
00:35:20,920 --> 00:35:23,520
I'll make sure
you don't have any descendants!

678
00:35:24,400 --> 00:35:26,610
If Little Wan'er asks about last night,

679
00:35:26,610 --> 00:35:27,440
just tell her

680
00:35:27,680 --> 00:35:30,410
we spent the whole night
investigating the case.

681
00:35:32,650 --> 00:35:33,740
Do you hear me?

682
00:35:35,650 --> 00:35:37,400
I do. I do.

683
00:35:38,130 --> 00:35:38,770
Plus,

684
00:35:39,730 --> 00:35:40,590
you must forget

685
00:35:40,870 --> 00:35:42,850
everything that happened last night.

686
00:35:42,850 --> 00:35:44,650
Don't ever think about it again!

687
00:35:48,130 --> 00:35:49,080
Ning,

688
00:35:49,730 --> 00:35:50,850
you're wrong.

689
00:35:51,560 --> 00:35:52,590
If I forget it,

690
00:35:53,610 --> 00:35:55,010
my mind will be all empty.

691
00:35:56,610 --> 00:35:58,610
If I'm not allowed to think about it,

692
00:35:59,810 --> 00:36:01,470
then I won't have to forget it.

693
00:36:10,260 --> 00:36:13,050
You two must've had great fun last night.

694
00:36:13,620 --> 00:36:16,230
Why not pay the bill now?

695
00:36:16,730 --> 00:36:17,320
Pay up.

696
00:36:27,040 --> 00:36:28,100
Where is the money?

697
00:37:13,580 --> 00:37:14,870
[Postmortem Report]

698
00:37:15,480 --> 00:37:16,340
Your Highness,

699
00:37:19,130 --> 00:37:20,860
here is the postmortem report.

700
00:37:22,920 --> 00:37:24,850
I have completed the examination.

701
00:37:25,290 --> 00:37:28,090
The victim's arms
wrapped around a bronze pillar.

702
00:37:28,760 --> 00:37:30,020
He was severely burned

703
00:37:30,250 --> 00:37:32,980
from the top of his head
to the bottoms of his feet.

704
00:37:33,320 --> 00:37:35,880
I'm not sure if Datura powder was used.

705
00:37:36,360 --> 00:37:37,160
That said,

706
00:37:37,330 --> 00:37:39,290
there are no signs of a struggle
on the body.

707
00:37:39,290 --> 00:37:42,040
Traces of powder were found in the lungs.

708
00:37:42,560 --> 00:37:43,290
I believe

709
00:37:44,040 --> 00:37:45,040
the victim

710
00:37:45,040 --> 00:37:47,480
had become unconscious
before the fire was on.

711
00:37:47,480 --> 00:37:49,770
The victim probably
died of smoke inhalation

712
00:37:49,770 --> 00:37:50,900
and burns to organs.

713
00:37:51,250 --> 00:37:53,170
On the back of the body

714
00:37:53,250 --> 00:37:54,920
and in the bed at the crime scene,

715
00:37:54,920 --> 00:37:56,780
I found a small amount of mercury.

716
00:37:57,300 --> 00:37:59,050
That was probably left

717
00:37:59,340 --> 00:38:02,070
after the cinnabar
in the red lead chalks burned.

718
00:38:05,730 --> 00:38:06,590
Your Highness,

719
00:38:07,440 --> 00:38:08,160
did I

720
00:38:08,540 --> 00:38:09,540
miss anything?

721
00:38:10,400 --> 00:38:12,660
You conducted a through check, Mr. Fang.

722
00:38:13,080 --> 00:38:13,960
I'm flattered.

723
00:38:15,000 --> 00:38:15,860
Your Highness,

724
00:38:16,850 --> 00:38:18,440
to be perfectly candid,

725
00:38:19,070 --> 00:38:21,270
despite my ten-odd years' experience,

726
00:38:22,360 --> 00:38:24,090
I remained a mediocre coroner.

727
00:38:24,340 --> 00:38:25,740
I didn't realize this job

728
00:38:26,140 --> 00:38:27,540
could save lives

729
00:38:28,080 --> 00:38:30,080
and restore justice for the society

730
00:38:30,160 --> 00:38:31,760
until I met you.

731
00:38:34,000 --> 00:38:36,250
I have no regrets anymore.

732
00:38:40,730 --> 00:38:42,260
Thank you for the hard work.

733
00:38:53,660 --> 00:38:54,810
Ouch! It hurts!

734
00:38:54,810 --> 00:38:55,770
Not so hard, Chi!

735
00:38:55,770 --> 00:38:57,040
-The two of you...
-I'll never do it again!

736
00:38:57,040 --> 00:38:58,810
One is a prince's heir,
and the other a princess.

737
00:38:58,810 --> 00:38:59,880
What a disgrace to fight

738
00:38:59,880 --> 00:39:01,540
in a brothel over a small bill!

739
00:39:01,560 --> 00:39:03,820
Do you even know what humiliation means?

740
00:39:04,130 --> 00:39:05,360
Not so loud.

741
00:39:05,400 --> 00:39:08,060
It'll be a bigger humiliation
if people hear us.

742
00:39:08,260 --> 00:39:09,120
What happened?

743
00:39:09,410 --> 00:39:10,610
-Nothing!
-Nothing!

744
00:39:11,960 --> 00:39:12,760
The two of them

745
00:39:15,830 --> 00:39:17,580
found a lead in Fengqi House.

746
00:39:18,360 --> 00:39:19,290
-Right!
-Right!

747
00:39:19,390 --> 00:39:20,790
Quite an important lead.

748
00:39:22,960 --> 00:39:24,080
The person who knows the three victims

749
00:39:24,080 --> 00:39:25,440
and has asked the girls

750
00:39:25,440 --> 00:39:26,970
at Fengqi House about them

751
00:39:27,230 --> 00:39:29,670
is the carver dismissed by Ranmo Gallery—

752
00:39:29,700 --> 00:39:30,900
-Wang Xin!
-Wang Xin!

753
00:39:31,470 --> 00:39:33,200
A carver doesn't get paid much.

754
00:39:33,320 --> 00:39:35,960
How can Wang Xin afford
frequent visits to Fengqi House?

755
00:39:35,960 --> 00:39:36,770
Little Wan'er,

756
00:39:36,770 --> 00:39:38,250
let me tell you something.

757
00:39:38,480 --> 00:39:40,360
Carvers go to brothels

758
00:39:40,440 --> 00:39:41,770
not to spend money,

759
00:39:42,070 --> 00:39:43,800
but to make money.

760
00:39:44,330 --> 00:39:45,860
The ladies there sometimes

761
00:39:45,870 --> 00:39:49,000
coax those pretentious scholars
into gifting them

762
00:39:49,020 --> 00:39:50,290
seals, jade pendants and such.

763
00:39:50,290 --> 00:39:52,330
When the carvers get paid,

764
00:39:52,330 --> 00:39:55,360
they'll share some profits
with the girls.

765
00:39:57,250 --> 00:39:59,000
Both sides will benefit.

766
00:40:00,250 --> 00:40:03,450
You seem quite familiar with
how things work in brothels.

767
00:40:03,920 --> 00:40:05,960
There's nothing about brothels

768
00:40:06,520 --> 00:40:07,170
that I...

769
00:40:07,170 --> 00:40:08,630
can't find out with money.

770
00:40:09,290 --> 00:40:10,960
Don't even get me started on it.

771
00:40:10,960 --> 00:40:12,520
If you hadn't squandered all the money,

772
00:40:12,520 --> 00:40:15,850
would I have had to wrestle with
those people in the brothel?

773
00:40:18,000 --> 00:40:20,080
Ning, Li,

774
00:40:20,080 --> 00:40:21,850
the information you got is very helpful.

775
00:40:21,850 --> 00:40:22,630
However,

776
00:40:23,080 --> 00:40:24,560
you got drunk during an investigation

777
00:40:24,560 --> 00:40:25,520
and nearly jeopardized our work.

778
00:40:25,520 --> 00:40:26,610
Merits offset faults.

779
00:40:26,610 --> 00:40:27,660
If you make one more blunder,

780
00:40:27,660 --> 00:40:29,360
I won't let you join me
in future investigations.

781
00:40:29,360 --> 00:40:30,170
Understood?

782
00:40:30,500 --> 00:40:31,600
-Understood.
-Understood.

783
00:40:31,600 --> 00:40:33,320
When I'm in the Ministry of War,

784
00:40:33,320 --> 00:40:34,580
you must keep Wan safe.

785
00:40:35,010 --> 00:40:37,010
Rest assured. With me and Ning here,

786
00:40:37,040 --> 00:40:39,100
Little Wan'er will be safe and sound.

787
00:40:42,000 --> 00:40:43,080
Don't worry.

788
00:40:43,110 --> 00:40:44,070
I'll go with them

789
00:40:44,100 --> 00:40:46,130
to visit Wang Shouchang's mother later.

790
00:40:46,130 --> 00:40:46,650
Okay.

791
00:40:51,880 --> 00:40:52,740
Little Wan'er,

792
00:40:52,960 --> 00:40:55,160
how did you know we got drunk last night?

793
00:40:55,830 --> 00:40:57,100
If not,

794
00:40:57,200 --> 00:40:59,470
how could your smell have got on him?

795
00:41:05,750 --> 00:41:07,010
I didn't say anything.

796
00:41:11,400 --> 00:41:12,850
To be honest, Your Highness,

797
00:41:12,850 --> 00:41:14,960
Shouchang used to be a naughty kid.

798
00:41:16,000 --> 00:41:17,060
At the age of eight,

799
00:41:17,560 --> 00:41:20,690
he burned down an abandoned hut
when he played with fire,

800
00:41:20,980 --> 00:41:22,070
without knowing

801
00:41:22,440 --> 00:41:25,000
an old beggar was in it,
hiding from the cold.

802
00:41:25,330 --> 00:41:26,730
He didn't realize it

803
00:41:27,040 --> 00:41:28,840
until screams reached his ears.

804
00:41:28,920 --> 00:41:30,960
By then, the blaze had become too intense.

805
00:41:30,960 --> 00:41:33,010
Shouchang wanted to rescue the beggar,

806
00:41:33,010 --> 00:41:34,140
but he got cold feet.

807
00:41:34,690 --> 00:41:37,090
Then that old beggar was unfortunately...

808
00:41:38,440 --> 00:41:40,250
What a terrible accident.

809
00:41:43,880 --> 00:41:45,810
Does anyone else know about this?

810
00:41:46,520 --> 00:41:47,690
No, I guess not.

811
00:41:48,130 --> 00:41:51,040
Not a day went by
without Shouchang feeling guilty.

812
00:41:51,650 --> 00:41:53,360
He became more and more quiet.

813
00:41:54,140 --> 00:41:57,140
But he did occasionally

814
00:41:57,160 --> 00:41:59,300
chat with a jade carver named Wang Xin,

815
00:41:59,470 --> 00:42:01,070
who worked in Ranmo Gallery.

816
00:42:02,050 --> 00:42:03,850
Shouchang shouldn't have died.

817
00:42:07,560 --> 00:42:08,960
Wang Shouchang set a fire and took a life.

818
00:42:08,960 --> 00:42:10,610
But that was an honest mistake.

819
00:42:10,610 --> 00:42:12,670
He was not an unscrupulous criminal.

820
00:42:13,360 --> 00:42:14,960
A man who sincerely repented on his wrongs

821
00:42:14,960 --> 00:42:16,520
was tortured and killed brutally.

822
00:42:16,520 --> 00:42:19,520
How can it be justified
as walking the "Heavenly Way"?

823
00:42:19,690 --> 00:42:22,490
The "Heavenly Way" is
defined by a man's thinking.

824
00:42:22,560 --> 00:42:24,290
If a man's thinking strays from
the right track,

825
00:42:24,290 --> 00:42:28,420
then walking the "Heavenly Way"
will become an excuse of lynching others.

826
00:42:28,730 --> 00:42:30,810
I wonder how many members there are
in the Heavenly Way Society.

827
00:42:30,810 --> 00:42:33,360
If every one of them kills innocent people
like Wang Xin does,

828
00:42:33,360 --> 00:42:35,560
won't that make the capital a living hell?

829
00:42:35,560 --> 00:42:38,000
I was going to tell Your Highnesses
about my findings.

830
00:42:38,000 --> 00:42:41,290
Based on the previously
calculated time of murders,

831
00:42:41,380 --> 00:42:43,010
I've roughly deduced

832
00:42:43,360 --> 00:42:45,810
the locations of the seven murders.

833
00:42:49,810 --> 00:42:51,940
How did you figure this out, Mr. Zhang?

834
00:42:58,640 --> 00:42:59,550
A compass?

835
00:43:00,830 --> 00:43:01,620
Exactly.

836
00:43:02,070 --> 00:43:03,680
Your Highnesses, do you know

837
00:43:03,710 --> 00:43:05,310
how the stars move in the sky?

838
00:43:07,730 --> 00:43:10,440
In ancient times,
the 24 solar terms were determined

839
